\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think so. But after that he - he was a greengrocer and he also had the farm - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he do any part time jobs when he had the farm?
