\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he do any decorating, repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think so. Mother mostly did that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he dress or undress or bath you or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have any jobs you had to carry out regularly at home to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well about this time my mother died. When I was nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And then what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well of course we had to help in the house. My father as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And the jobs you had to do after your mother died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had to do the cleaning up and the washing and - helping with anything there was to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you help take care of your younger brother and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of things would you have to do for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Help to bath them. And about that time a neighbour took my youngest sister away, she was only six weeks old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When your mother died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they keep her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. They kept her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they legally adopt her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well yes, but they'd - they always had her - right up to her marriage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You can't remember if there was any question of your relatives taking her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, we all were in bed very early.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that because it was a farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you share a bedroom or bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 With my sister. My eldest sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did your brother sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In the same room in another bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - downstairs in front of the kitchen fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How often did you bath?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was there a special day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Saturday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When did you have clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I suppose - at the weekend. For Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In the - in the kitchen. Yes, it was a living-kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where was the cooking done - was it a range or gas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 It was a - no, it was a range, a coal - a coal and fire never went out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have breakfast there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. All our meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you all eat together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. We all ate together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You told me about washing - you had to go down and get water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, from the well. We always had to get out water from the well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Winter and summer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. We'd no water laid on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And that was every morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember what you had for breakfasts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Mostly bacon and eggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was there anything different on certain days such as Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we'd mostly bacon and eggs for breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the midday meal, was that the big meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - lots of - what we used to call hash. It was like a stew, plenty of boiled puddings made with suet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was in the middle of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What would the evening meal be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well for tea we might have a boiled egg or jam or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that the last meal of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we used to have supper.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Mostly it was bread and milk. Boiled milk with bread in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was your own milk from the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That - yes. Had all our own milk and butter and eggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your mother or father bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 We'd be speaking about your step-mother now would we?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she make her own jam and preserves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Bottle fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And wine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And did she make medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh raspberry vinegar and elderberry syrup and - all that kind of thing, rhubarb wine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your father brew beer at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Oh they brew - one brewed. They did brew their own beer, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they grow their own vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well they grew all their own vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You never had tinned or dried fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Not at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you keep any livestock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Pigs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, we always had our own pig to be killed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And chickens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And our own fowls, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember how many times a week you ate meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - two or three times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In addition to the bacon for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was all your own bacon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Bacon, yes, but we bought the meat from the butcher. He called twice a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And you had meat?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 From him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you ever have extra meat from hunting or poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well, no, except rabbits. He used to shoot rabbits on the farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 On his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, on our own farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you ever remember seeing your step-mother having less food so the family could have more, did your father have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I think they - there seemed to be enough for all of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, we weren't allowed to talk during meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we had to have what was given to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What would be your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 My father used to say, it'll come out the next meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 If there was something on the table you want like the salt, could you ask someone to pass it to you or did you have to wai
t until it was offered?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - I never used to see any sauce - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way and sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. My father was very particular about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you bring toys or books to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Definitely not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When could you leave the table - did you have to wait?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 We had to ask when we finished if we could leave the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you always have the same places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember how the meal was served, did you mother serve from the range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What order were you served in?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I think it was dad first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When the children were very young were they fed separately or did they sit with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, he always sat to the table. In between my mother dying I think my father was about two years before he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587  again. But during that period we had several housekeepers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were they paid housekeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember if they were local women?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 At the time of your mother's death can you remember any relatives came and helped, she was ill wasn't she for a little while?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember if any of them offered any help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Nobody came in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 To be with you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Except the neighbour next door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The one that adopted your sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 But both your parents came from there, was there nobody who could come in, your father's mother for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh she could occasionally but she had - thirteen children to look after. And he was the eldest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was your step-mother affectionate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Very.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And she showed affection to you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Very much so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 If you had any worries could you share them with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I shouldn't share them with him, he was too strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Very little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well of course we had to be very obedient.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about your parents ideas on the way you should behave towards your brother and sisters - d
id they say you should hit back or not if another child hit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we weren't supposed to quarrel or fight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your parents have any idea of the sort of people they wanted you to be, did they bring you up to consider certain things important?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. going to chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was this your mother or father mostly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 My father. He was - a very strict Methodist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 This influenced everything did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did he think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh we never heard such a word in our house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When grown-ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 If you did something your parents disapproved of what would happen to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well my father would beat us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How often would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well if he found out we'd done anything wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about your step-mother, did she ever punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, never. She used to - keep us from getting whipped, she was very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you remember any particular occasion when you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Once when I didn't come s
traight home from - chapel. My father came to look for me and - it was rather - well, we wouldn't call it late now but it was about eight o'clock and of course he whipped me very hard. I remember that very plainly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you remember how you felt about being punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, I used to say I should run away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would you say that both your parents influenced you the same with the ideas about how to behave or was one more important than the other?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well of course we always had such a fear of my f
ather, fear we were doing wrong you see that we - we tried not to do things that weren't right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you get any presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Anything special to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Any guests?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we never had any playmates to come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Nobody visited the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember anything special you did with your mother and father on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, no, we just had the ordinary Christmas dinner 
and - people used to come round singing. The choir from the chapel used to come around to sing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Then you went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. We had to go every Sunday - four times a day. Sunday school in the morning. Sunday school in the afternoon and out o
f Sunday school into the chapel 'til four o'clock and then again back again at six at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 With dinner in between?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, dinner in between and tea of course. And we - we had to go because my father was choirmaster and he knew whether we went or not.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So that was your Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was our Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have any musical instruments in your home? Did anybody play or sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not much except my father had a - a fiddle, the violin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And he played that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, in his wa
y of course. Well he wasn't very good you know. We often used to go up to my grandma's and the boys each had a musical instrument and we really enjoyed that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And they danced?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And sang together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Sang, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 These would be your father's brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Uncles, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you say they did the clog dance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh one of them did yes. And one had nicker nack as he called them. Bones. You know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of instruments did they play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 One had a - a fiddle as I say and - they had a - cello.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well, on Saturday night we used to play dominoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The whole family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Including your father?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, he did on Saturday nights.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. We weren't allowed to have anything to read.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What was his attitude to reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not a newspaper in - he said it was a waste of time. Could find us something better to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you remember your mother or father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not much. Only the local paper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they ever read aloud to your or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you remember a funeral in the family when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Remember is my grandfather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember who came to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well, was quite a lot of relatives, being a large family you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that your father's father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they wear mourning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. I always - just remember that you always used to have wine and biscuits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would that be at hour house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. At me grandfather's house. At the funeral. I remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you taking out visiting neighbours, friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, only to - an old aunt of me father's and me grandmother's, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you tell me a bit about your visits with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I can't tell you much about it except they were just - went for tea occasionally and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you do when you went there - did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we just had to sit quietly. When we went for tea we had to stand around the table, we hadn\rquote t to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You didn't visit anybody else that you can remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No. No. I do - I do remember going to see some distant relatives, very old they were and they had some hand weaving and we had to go up some steps outside the house to get to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And was he actually weaving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. With candles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember what he was making?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. I don't know. Some kind of hand looms.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You'd be very young then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh very - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember going shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Oh yes. We had to shop as we came home from school. We had to take the cows into the field as we were going to school, sometimes we had to come and bring them back at night, sometimes we had to go another way and a call and bring the shopping home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 From the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. There was only one shop, that was my grandfather's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He owned the village shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of things would you buy there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Everything. It was the Post Office and - well you could get anything. Paraf
fin to pocket handkerchiefs. Anything you can mention, sweets - food for the cattle, potatoes and any - anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember any longer shopping expeditions? To {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Huddersfield{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, no, the only place I can remember going was {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Barnsley{\*\xmlclose}. We 
used to take eggs there on market day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have to help sell the eggs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. I used to have to help to wash them - pack them ready for going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was one of your jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And then we went in a - what was it - horse and we sat on either side you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Like a cart?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 A wagon - a wagonette, but - I don't know what you'd call it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How long would it take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - about an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was a days outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. It were a most peculiar thing this we had to go up steps to get into it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you go just with your father then or did your step-mother come with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, because mother used to do some shopping there you see while they were there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you remember going out just with your father anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about Bank Holidays and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we knew any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What happened when school was out in the summer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had to work in the fields.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of work would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well - chopping the thistles down and picking stones out of the - mowing grass fields before the machines went in. See, and then in the summer of course we had to help with the hay making.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh we used to go up in the mornings and stay all day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you cutting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, it was cutting - we had to keep - it was put into rows and we had to keep turning it over one day and turning it over the next.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What tools would you use for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Brigs. Then - they put it into long rows and then put it into haycocks. Then it was ready for - then it stood and dried.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Even the children helped with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. And mother used to bring our meals up to the fields. It was very hot. I can remember that, how hot it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was Saturday any different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no. Only cleaning. Giving a good clean in the house and outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And you helped with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Trimming all the lamps because we had paraffin lamps, all the lamps had to be cleaned on Saturday afternoons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about other jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Yes. Helping with the churning. My father used to put us - stand on a stool because I wasn't tall enough to reach the handle. We had to churn when we - that was when we came from school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 After school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have Sunday clothes, different clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, we had Sunday clothes, yes. We were all - we all had to go to Sunday school, in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your father think it wrong to work on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, we weren't allowed to use a pair of scissors on Sunday in our house. Nor stitch a button on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, not on Sunday. It was a sin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your mother also go to the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes - Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The whole family?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And you went to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And chapel twice a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you tell me about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we just - just once a year that's all, in the summe
r. We only went as far as Humley. From Hollinswain - so that wasn't very far you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well there was a lake there and we used to boat and - and some round about you know and swings and things, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And have tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. It wasn't much of a place but it was an outing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would the chapel have any other social activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, they had concerts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You went to those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, we had to go to those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And your brother and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Me sister did, I don't remember me brother did but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did the chapel run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were any of you members of a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. But we weren't allowed to have anything to drink of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 There was no alcohol in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you belong to any other clubs organised by the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, because there wasn't anything. Nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, always. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. But we had to say our prayers.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your father read from the Bible or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think he did. But still he was - you know - good living man I should imagine, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well, yes, but we weren't allowed to know anything about it. We could never find out what we - what we were you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You don't know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I always thought he was a Liberal but - we never really knew.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 If he was why do you think he had those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I've no idea at all because he never discussed it with us you know at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about your mother, do you think she was interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you ever remember them voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, he - I remember them going to vote but I don't know what they did vote.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When your parents weren't working on the farm or going to chapel how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, just - doing farm - the farm work that's all and - walk around the fields. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your step-mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she ever go out just to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, there was no where to go you see, except just for a walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she have any special friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Because she came from - a long way off, she wasn't a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11940834\charrsid16649587 local}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She wasn't a local girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No. She sometimes had some of her relatives to visit us. Not often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember what time your father came in in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well he used to go on different turns you see. Sometimes he worked through the night and came home about five in the morning then of course he had to start the farm work you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He was still working in the mine was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, at that - one period he was, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you say how many evenings a week he'd be at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How many evenings? Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He didn't go to pubs or clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he ever take part in any sport?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Only going round shooting - rabbits and things like that in the fields.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you know if either of them belonged to any savings club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. I'm sure they didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Funeral club or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No. Oh my father'd belong to the - would it be the Odd Fellowes club. He did. I don't remember him ever going to any meetings. Suppose he'd have to pay subscription but - that was as far as he went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did you get on with your older sister and your younger brother, were you particularly close to either one of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not particularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who did you play with most - you said playmates didn't come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. You had to play with each other but we hadn't much time to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When you did where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In the fields. In the woods.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember the games you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Jumping across a brook in the wood - falling in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Is there anything else you can remember - marbles or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Oh we used to play - marbles, yes, and - rounders, what we called rounders. But not much time you know for playing. Father always used to find us something to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh we had to get clean before we went in the house if we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your parents ever discourage you from playing with certain children or was it just because you were so far away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well for one thing we were far - pretty far away but - he never encouraged anyone to come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 It doesn't sound as if you had much time or anything like hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about pets or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we hadn't any pets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you go for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not often. We used to go into the fields that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about sports? You were telling me about hoops once?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well that was - you know, hoop with a stick to make it run, that's all. Not much of a game.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about theatres?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, there was nothing of that kind because we lived about
 three miles from - the nearest place and there was no theatre there and the doctor lived there. We had to walk, there was no bus.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was the next village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, Penistone. And - we were about three miles away. Nothing - I remember only once going to anything there and there was a circus.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In Penistone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me a bit about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I can't remember much about it because I got lost. You see, we were never allowed far away from home and I'd never been before and - 
when I came out I didn't know the way home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So really the only entertainments would be the concerts at chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That's all. And the chapel concerts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh we never had any pocket money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You didn't get a regular amount?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we might have got a ha'penny a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you spend that on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh what did I - I said - aniseed balls or - kali - lemon kali or something like that. And it had to last us all week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did any of your relatives ever give you money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No. I remember my grandfather once giving - oh - at the feast, it was supposed to be the feast once a year, he'd give us threepennybit. And then we weren't allowed to go to either a dance or anything like that you know. My father didn't be
lieve in that. Nor they didn't believe in cards, there were never any cards in the house
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Just the dominoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Dominoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What would have happened if your step-mother was ill or in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had to do - we had to do all we could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Nobody came in to help her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your parents have any friends in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not - not anyone that used to come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your step-mother have friends of her own from where she came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well, as I say, she had them - they came once or twice to visit her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And then they would stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 People often say that in those days they made their own amusements, do you think this was true in your case?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I think so, yes, because there was nothing - no where
 to go at all. Except to church and chapel that's all - all there was. Feed the hens and collect the eggs. And all that sort of thing. Get the potatoes boiled for the pigs to eat and - it was all - it was all sort of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember how you thought of the people around you, some belonging to one group and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, they were all pretty much the same, you know, they were mostly old farmers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who else would there be in the village besides the farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Nothing really. No,
 there was no - no kind of works, they had to go to Penistone to the steel works or a place called the band mill but there was nothing in Hollinswain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was it your grandfather who had the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And the Post Office, it was all one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Among the farmers were there some that had bigger farms than others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - just - I think there was only really one that lived anywhere around us, was a bigger one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So you'd say your family belonged to the same group as the other people in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember at that time being brought up to treat anybody any differently from anybody else - did you have to curtsey to anybody?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, nothing of that kind, except the vicar. No - no different much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In the district around can you say who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, there wasn't - there wasn't anyone any different, they were all pretty much alike. I don't think - I don't think there was anyone.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well there was only the one shopkeeper and th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11940834\charrsid16649587 at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587  was my grandfather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the schoolteachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't know. Used - like an ordinary person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of people would you say went to the church as opposed to the chapel - there was a church wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, there was a church - I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587  at the church. Well they were all pretty much the same. They were village people. I don't think anyone - thought themselves any better than anyone else. Yes, it was a - quite a sleepy place as you say you
 know, there was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were there any families that were considered rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I can't say that there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You say your step-mother came from much further away, do you think she saw herself as belonging to a particular group or class different?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No, I don't think so. She liked the place very much when she came to live with us. But I - I know really a great deal about my own mother. The only thing I can remember I think was my brother being born 'cos I stayed away from school and and got int
o trouble.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Because I ought to have been at school and I wanted to stay at home to see this new baby you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you remember seeing a policeman around the village when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, we had one, just one, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they frighten you with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No, we were always very friendly with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How do you think he treated people in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I think he was very kind because - I mean, I don't think he ever had any trouble with anyone in the village, I don't think so at all.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you remember ever feeling that your parents had to struggle very hard to make a living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I don't think they were too well off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you say a bit more about that? Your father was carrying two jobs at one time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, after he left the pit he started this greengrocery you see. No, I - I think we were fairly comfortable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you given lessons by your parents at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I should think about five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When you first started what time did you have to go in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Leave home do you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, and get to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well half past eight. For nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And when did you get back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well, depended what we had to do on the way home, if we had to get - collect the cattle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You stayed for dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, we had to take sandwiches. Oh yes, I always remember taking my dinner. We used to go in th
e woods and - eat it. There, sit in the wood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What kind of school was it, was it a church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 It had boys and girls?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Mixed school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How long did it take you to get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - almost half an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 It was quite a way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Quite a long way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you go alone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Sister and I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you think of school, did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I liked some of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the teachers, how many teachers were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well it was only a small school, there was one very big room where all the upper classes were and then a small infant room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They had their own teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember what the teachers emphasized as being important, were they strict about manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, they were very - very strict. We - we didn't learn a lot there. It was just reading, writing and arithmetic and sewing of course.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they try and change your way of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no. No. Nothing. No grammar was taught there or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about being on time and tidy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh we had to be on time or else we were punished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of punishment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had to hold our hands out and have the cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The girls the same as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, and the boys got it across his knee.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 For what sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Depended what they'd done - I don't know really. But if we were late or - if we were rough, you know, if it was wet and we couldn't go out to play we used to play in the porch and if we made a lot of noise and were rough they used to punish us like that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They didn't ask about it at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't remember them doing at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did the other children come from similar homes to yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember if the teachers singled out some children and treated them differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were there gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I think - we were all pretty much the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about children who were left out by the other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well of course we always used to be having quarrels but - soon made it up again,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You left from that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 'Til I was eleven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And then you didn't go on to any other school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would you have stayed longer if you could have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I don't think there was any question about it at all. We - we just had to leave to get some work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you go to any education classes after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. I went into service when I was eleven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - I have done in later years but not at that time, didn't worry me. Because we knew who had to start and earn our own living, that's
 all there was to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was there any place that anybody could have gone from that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Penistone. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Penistone{\*\xmlclose} 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Grammar school{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. But I don't remember anyone going at all. Yes, they all seemed to leave about that age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said you were always working at home, did you ever work outside for any money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No. Just an errand for a neighbour, that's all. But we weren't allowed to earn money with it. Was to be done as a kindness.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You left school at eleven, can you tell me what you did then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I went to live - near {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Huddersfield{\*\xmlclose}. With a schoolmaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How many servants were there there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 None except myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What were you called there, were you just a general?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 There? I slept in, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember where - in the attic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think they had an attic. Small bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 On your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you eat? With the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your mistress supervise all the housework?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did you feel with the members of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I don't know. Do you know I can't remember much about that at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was your first time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And I stayed there you know, I don't think I was there very long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What kind of family was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They were young - young children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh get up and light the fires and help with the cooking. Clean the shoes and - do general housework.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You were only eleven at the time, did the lady of the house take an interest in you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not very much. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you go out when you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no. Just an afternoon out into town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you feel homesick there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Very. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have any companion-s at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the children in the household?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I used to take the - out sometimes you know, the children but - that's as far as I got.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You were only there a short time, what about your second job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh well I went much further away from home there. And they were two elderly people. They kept a shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you know how these jobs were found?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I suppose they were found through an agency. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And in the second job what did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh well, it was more like being at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - she was a maiden lady and she treated me like a - a child, in fact, I got a bit fed up with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me a bit about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well she used to put me in a chair and wrap me up you know and make a fuss of me. I - I didn't have a lot to do there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were there any other servants in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she do some of the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, she helped me with the work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of things did you have to do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well just the washing up and dusting and tidying the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were they retired people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And they just kept this small shop, sweetshop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about friends there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I didn't have any at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she let you go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, if I liked I could just go out but you know when - I didn't know anyone so I didn't get far a field.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 But you felt she took an interest in you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, she looked after me all right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember how long you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, about six months I think and then I left there and went to a - another house in the same locality and - had a much harder life there.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember why you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No I don't - I don't know why I left at all, I never did know why I left there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You'd be about thirteen by then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, I should think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said this next place was much harder?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Very hard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you have to do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You were a general again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. They only - the only ser - the only o
ne and they kept a boot shop and there were three children in the family and - one of the girls wasn't very nice. Anyhow I had to work very hard there. Do the - the whole weeks washing. Oh yes, I used to go down in the cellar about six o'clock in the morn
ing and start washing. All the washing was done at home. And the baking and everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who did the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I had to help.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said there were some children in the house, did they have to do anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, they didn't do anything.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How old would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well - the eldest was older than me. The girl was about my age and then there was a younger boy. Of course when I'd done in the house I had to go and help in the shop to clean the shelves you see. Take all the boxes o
ut and dust them. So I hadn't much chance to go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember much about the household, who dealt with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh the mother looked after them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about going to bed, did the older help the younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I had to help to get the boy to bed. The boy, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about bathing them and all that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I think they did that themselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, well we all had our meals together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You ate with the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember whether they had a gas cooker or did they use a range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I think they used a range. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they get up early?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes. Shop was open in good time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me what you did every day sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well of course I had to start with the fires and the washing up and the bed making and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did they have for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I can't remember - bacon mostly. Or porridge, they used a lot of porridge. Cocoa.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about dinners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, they had hot dinner in the middle of the day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You had the same food as they had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they make their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Baked their own bread, yes. I think that was where I learnt to bake bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she make jam and bottle and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. I don't think she did a lot of that. See, she looked after the shop mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she teach you anything - you said you learnt to bake there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, just a bit, yes, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were the children allowed to talk at mealtimes, can you remember how they behaved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, they were rather quarrel some, the boy and the girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could they choose what they wanted to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, it was put on the table and - they had to have what was given to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were they fussy about their manners at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No, I don't think they were very particular. You know, they weren't what I call better class people at all. Much about - I don't remember much about them at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They weren't very kind. Well I must have been there quite a while because I was sixteen when I went to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 About three years? Did you take the children out at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, they went to school you know. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember anything about their life, did they visit, did they have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think they had a great many. They were big chapel people and the eldest girl was in the choir, she was a good singer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they go on holiday and did you ever go with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no. I don't remember them going away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said they were big chapel people - did they keep Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they think it was wrong to work on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, belonged to the Band of Hope, do remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And the children went to church and Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you go with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't think I did there. No. I think I was too busy - getting the dinner ready.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember anything else about the master and mistress, did they go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No, they didn't. No. See they - they were just working people and when they - you know, either cleaning the shop out or busy doing other things. They didn't go out a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember why you left this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't know why I left I'm sure. I was tired of it I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What was your relation with the children, did you have much to do with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not very much. I hadn't much time.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said you shared a room with one of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I had to sleep with one - in the same room as the girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was she near your age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, she would be, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you friendly at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not very. She wasn't a very nice - girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the mistress, did she take an interest in you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not very much, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you say roughly what hours you worked there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The hours - it sort of never ended, it went on all day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have special times when you were off at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I don't think so except I think one time I used to go to the Band of Hope. I think it was on a Monday evening. Straight there and back.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 But there was no time during the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And when you were sixteen did you go home between jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well just for a short time. Not long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember how you got the next job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Through the Registry Office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not through somebody that you knew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me a little bit about that job when you first went there? What kind of a house was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh quite a big house and they kept three maids and a foot - coachman. There was only just the - master and his wife, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did he do, what was his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I was supposed to look after her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did the other servants do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well there was 
the cook and the parlourmaid and then I had to help the parlourmaid in the evening with the - table. Setting the table and helping to take the meals in. And if she - when she was going out I had to go and help to get her ready, put her shoes on and - hand
 her clothes and help her to get off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they do a lot of entertaining?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, a great deal, yes. You always had dinner in the evening, about half past seven. For course meal, whether they were alone or not.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they dress for dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, you always dressed for dinner, even if they were alone.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you have to wear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - print dress in the morning and then a black dress and apron in the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have to get that yourself or did they provide it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
I think they must have provided he uniforms. And - there was no washing done at home, at the house. It all went to the laundry - maids clothes as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you give me a rough idea of your day there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, well we had to get up about seven a
nd the first thing I had to do was to prepare tea and take it up to their bedrooms. The morning cup of tea. To both of them, yes. And then - then of course they got - he got up for breakfast, she didn't. She never got up for breakfast. He always had it al
one and got off to the mill, they were manufacturers. And he didn't come home 'til the evening. For dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you have to do next?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She - she used to get up and go out for a drive in the pony cart, of course there wasn't any - motors then, 
and she used to drive herself round the shops giving the orders. Then she'd come into the kitchen and make the menu out for the day for the evening meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 About what time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - about half past eleven I should say when she did that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What was your morning work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well I had to help with the - clearing the bedrooms with the parlourmaid. And then - she had a light lunch and usually either went and had a rest or she went out paying calls in the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you eat your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh we always ate in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you eat before them or after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, always after them. What they had we were - we were allowed to have the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 For breakfast for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh for breakfast, well - we had what they had, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And for lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we had a light lunch and then we had - our supper when they'd had theirs in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh it'd be getting on for half past eight when we had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So they would dine about eight o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Half past seven they had their meal. And of course we had to clear and all the - all the silver was taken into the housemaids pantry and done separately, the glasses and the silver. And the rest was taken into the kitchen to be washed up with the cook.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you do after lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well always after lunch we had an hours rest. The maids all had an hours rest. She said we needed it before the evening rush came on.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you have this rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh, in the kitchen with our feet up on a chair we had it there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the coachman, what did he do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Oh he - he - well he used to come in and help with the - he washed all the - pans and the dishes that went in the kitchen. He helped with those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You say your main work was in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, our hardest part was in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me what you had to do if they were entertaining?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh you mean - when we had to take the meals in? Of course everything had to be handed round to 
everyone separately, every dish. Starting from the master's right hand and working round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you learn all this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I learnt it there as I went on watching the other girl, she was much older than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she give you any tips?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, not much, I just used to do what she did, follow her around.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 After the big meal was over and it was washed up did you have any more duties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, only - getting our own supper and clearing away, then we didn't do anything else except a
bout ten o'clock we had to take, what we call take glasses in, take the whisky and soda.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Into the drawing room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Into the drawing room, yes. They always had that afterwards. And we had to go and light the gas fire - in her bedroom, turn the beds 
down ready for - for her to go to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They didn't have a lot of fires then for you to see to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, it was central heated.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No open fires at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No, they just had one in the morning room but it was central heated all over the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So the coachman would see to the boilers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Yes. He did the boiler work which the boiler was outside away from the house. Even the - conservatory was heated, it was - oh beautifully warm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was she interested in her maids?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh she was ve
ry nice, very nice indeed. If we weren't so well she - always said we were to go and lie down. Get something hot and go and lie down. She was very easy to live with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did they call you - by your last name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No, by our own name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 By your first names?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 All the women servants?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Only she - she called not - she didn't call me Edith like I was - I should have been because she had a friend called Edith so she called me Annie, which is my middle name, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said the parlourmaid was much older than you was the cook also older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. They were both older than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did you get on with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Very well with the cook, I liked her very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well not too - not too well with the parlourmaid. She wasn't very helpful either.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you share rooms with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
And the unfortunate thing was I slept in the same room as her. In fact in the same bed. Yes. The cook had a room to herself. I had to share with the other one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You say you had an hours rest in the afternoon, what about other times off - did you go out at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I - I wasn't allowed to have a night out, they said I was too young. I had an afternoon. And - and Sunday afternoon as well. Oh, I wen
t to church with them on Sunday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They went to the church, not the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They went to the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that your choice or did they want you to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, it wasn't my choice, I had to go with them you see on Sunday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did the cook and the parlourmaid had to go with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. They didn't go. I think it was because I was younger you see. She said I wasn't old enough to go out alone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you do on your afternoon off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Just stroll around looking at the shops, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have any friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. We were never allowed any friends in. None whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How far was this place from your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Miles I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 About twelve miles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you get home very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Not very often. About once a month perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have any relatives in Holmfirth?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Nobody I knew at all. A while after I went there my sister came to live in Holmfirth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was she also in service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She wasn't in the same house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not at that time. But she came to be cook there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How many years after you'd been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I think about two years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And then the older cook left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And your sister came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And what about the older parlourmaid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The parlourmaid died. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you become parlourmaid then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I had to, yes, 'til they got someone else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So there was still three of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, they got someone else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who trained your sister to cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't know, she just went by books I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of thing did she have to cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - everything. I couldn't tell you. She had a great big stove that you could put, I should think, a dozen pans on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was it a coal fire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, it was coal. Or coke, I don't know which.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They didn't cook on gas then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No. In the spring they always went abroad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 For how long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 About two months I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they close the house down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, we were left there. We had t
o - do the spring cleaning then. Part of the time and - then when we'd done it we could go home. 'Til they were ready for coming back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were you paid during that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, we were paid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who was in charge of the house while they were away?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - no one really except us. The maids.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They didn't mind - they considered you quite young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well you see the cook and - and the parlourmaid were older than me, much older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So they were supposed to keep you in order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 But it still went on the same when - after my sister came. We just did the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you do when they were away besides spring cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well there was plenty to do you know, it was a large house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they have a vacuum cleaner at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Do you know, I can't remember about that at all. The carpets were all take up during that period and the coachman - and another man used to take them out. And - clean them and put them back again, we didn't have to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was it mostly wood floors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, all wood floors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So they were really just rugs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, that's right. Oh yes, well we - we used to enjoy ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Doing this spring cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 All amongst the spring cleaning we used to have lots of fun. Put the pianola on and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And have dancing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Oh yes, we used to be dancing about because there was no one to tell us how quick we'd to be or anything, we could just do it in our own time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Then you could take a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How long were you there in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Four years. Twenty-first birthday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She gave you a silver watch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So you'd be there at least five years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, about that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me a little bit more about life in that house, was it quite formal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Everything had to be done just the same - whether there was a party of not. All the meals had to be carried in and handed round just the same. And the wines.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How many courses did they have in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When they were alone? Oh, only about three when they were alone. Of course they'd have much more if they'd visitors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they have house guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes. Quite a few.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You would wait on them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Just the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have to attend the lady house guests as a personal maid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, I had to go and help get their dresses out ready for them you know and - brush their hair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have to see their clothes at all, mending and cleaning and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes, that was one thing I had to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And where did you learn about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Nowhere. It was no special - sewing and I mean not dressmaking or anything like that, just - I had to see to the linen and - if there's anything wanted mending which wasn't very often. Was supposed 
to go about with our eyes and ears shut, we weren't supposed to see anything, that's it. When you're in a place like that you're not supposed to - to - know anything and I think that's why they wouldn't allow you to have friends you see. Because it would 
be talked about in the village. I - I think that's why. They wouldn't want their affairs talking about you see, outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 But you knew things weren't too good between them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - well - oh yes, well of course I mean the cook and the parlourmaid had
 been there so long they knew everything and - I - they talked to me about it so - I soon got to know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did it upset you when you found out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well of course - at first I was - being so young I was a bit shocked. But - I soon got used to it, that I didn't mind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said she was a good mistress in the sense of being interested in you, would you say she was a good mistress as a manager?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, definitely, very good manager. Very good manager.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did she keep track of the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well she used to go into the - pantry where she kept all her food - practically every day and always put - if anything was taken out it was always replaced. Always plenty of food in. Oh she was an exceptionally good manager. Of course she had to provide f
or such a lot of visitors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You felt there was enough money behind them to do this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. They were very well to do. In fact, she was presented at court you know. He collect quite a lot of money when he died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You stayed there five years and then what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Why - well I wasn't well and I had to go home. I was at home quite a while. And then I came back to Home - the village and - to her cousin. I went there as childrens nurse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You were recommended by her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You t
old me the people you worked for before were mill owners - he was a mill manager, could you tell me a bit more about their social position?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - I don't know what really you mean.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would you say they were important people in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes. There weren't many more families like them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who were these visitors they had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well mostly the visitors that they had to stay were from London and different places. People they'd met when they were abroad, when they'd been on the voyage you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
You said in the village you grew up in there were very little social differences, most people were alike, farmers and so on, when you came to this bigger village and worked for mill owners, how did you feel about their position?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh well - I don't know. Just - just had to take it that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you notice the difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well not much except all the - the girls at the village there worked in the mills, this man had two mills. 'Course we weren't allowed to mix with them. 
They thought we were inferior and she said we were - we were much better than them but we weren't allowed to mix with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did you think of these girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well of course we never came in contact with them hardly at all. Except the - the gardeners daughters, they were on the grounds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they work in the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, they both worked in the mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you make friends with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not much, no, they had their own friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When they had visitors in the house how did the visitors treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh, very well. Yes, they were very nice most of them. 'Course they had a lot of men friends came. More than - more than women.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have much to do with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not really. Except just to - see that the bedrooms were kept in order and - not much else, we didn't have to do with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you know as a mill owner did he do anything in the village, was he in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't think so. No, I think he was just his - his life's work, his mill. Spent all his days there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they hunt or go to the theatre?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, he did. He went hunting with his brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh she didn't. She didn't do much of anything except just pay calls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did she paint?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She didn't play the piano or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, she played the piano and sang. She was very nice pianist. For her own pleasure that's all, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they go out together a good deal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When they went out for dinner, yes, they always went together. But you see, he didn't spend much time at home during the day. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you think they were pleased with their position in life or do you think they wanted to go higher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I don't think so. No, I think they were quite content where they were. I don't there 
were any - anyone else in the place, they were in a better position than they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you tell me about the family where you went next - her cousin?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - when I went there it was very different because they had children. And the other plac
e there - there weren't any children at all. Of course it was much harder because there was only the cook and myself and - we had everything to do. And they weren't so well off either. And of course she was very young, she was only two years older than I 
was and she wasn't such a very good manager.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well - we were always short of something, always short of - food, if we asked for a thing she used to say, what again? Are we out of that again? As if I - we always used to think she hadn'
t enough money to go on with, I don't know, or else she didn't know how to spend it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about your meals then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had sometimes very poor meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you eat with the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no - no. We ate in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you eat the same food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we - we did if there was anything left but more often than not there wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So what did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Anything that we could get.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did the other servants stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. I think while I was there they had about four dif
ferent cooks. She never got a good cook who knew how to cook. Mostly I had to help. And bread was baked at home and I had to make that. The only thing was we had a - a woman came to wash.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And she washed at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She washed there at the home - at our home - place, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How often did she come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She'd wash for everybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She washed for everybody and I think she had half a crown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the babies washing, did you have to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Only just the nappies of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How old were the children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well when I went - the girl was eighteen months old and they had another just after I went. So of course I had to do everything for that one. Bath her and dress her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you feed her or did the mother feed her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, she was fed from the bottle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So you fed her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And then I had to take her out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember who taught you to do these things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No. I always remember the first time I bathed her, I was terrified.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did she feed on then, was it cows milk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Baby? Now what was it that she used to mix. Bengers and beat an egg up in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They didn't boil milk the way they do now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well of course it was boiled, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you boil the bottle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, they had to be sterilized, yes. And they always beat an egg up in it. That was my job, to look after her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they have a nursery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh they had a place where the children kept, yes, in a nursery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did the children have their meals upstairs or with their parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, in the nursery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have to keep those rooms clean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. I had to clean the rooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you sleep in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In the - upstairs on the same floor as they did at the back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have your own room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. We had two beds, the other girl and I slept in the same room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who attended to the baby and the little girl at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - sometimes I had to get up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did the mother have to do with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well she just did her shopping and - sort of messed about you know. I don't think she was very strong really. She'd had a very bad illness at one time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they go on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - she went once or twice but I don't - I don't remember ever them going away together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You never went with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Or the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I won't say that, no. We did once go to. Llandudno for three weeks. Her mother was there and we went and took the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you do the same things for them on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, I had to look after the children, wash their things and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about time off when you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 We had - I had one night off and every other Sunday afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you go to church with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. I went to church - on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you go to the church then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Which was quite near.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they go to church, did they keep Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not every Sunday, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So you were allowed to go out on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What was his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He was a doctor. So of course he - he was mostly on the - on the spot you see, he couldn't go away very far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What other interests did they have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think they did. They just - visited the other people around.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did they get on with their cousins, the mill manager?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Oh they - she was very friendly with her cousin. Used to visit. Yes. It all struck me that she was - trying to do the same as her cousin but of course - she hadn't the money and - she couldn't do it. And having children as well, made quite a difference.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How old was the eldest child when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - about eighteen months when I went and I was there - years I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So she was about four?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I should think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who was in charge of training her and disciplining her and manners and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I suppose her parents. No one else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How much did you have to do with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I had her constantly 'cos when I washed and - did - and that I had to take them out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you read to them and play with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, in the nursery. Mother of course used to go out into the village doing her shopping and paying her calls like they all did.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember an example of your day in that house, what did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well, just getting up and - preparing, well, the cook prepared the breakfast and then I took it in for them. Then we had to start with the cleaning of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You helped with the cleaning as well as the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, because there was only the cook you see to do the other work. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you do that when the children were a sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, they used to go down for a rest and - then I did it, well and they had run about while I was doing it. Yes. She didn't do much a
t all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they have their big meal in the middle of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No, they had more of a light lunch middle of the day and then they had what they called a cooked meal at night, it was never to me very much, not a big meal like we used to have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did the children eat what you ate at dinner time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No, they had their own meals. Separately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you eat after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, we ate after them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he come home for dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about in the afternoon, you took the children out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, I always took the children out for a walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And then what did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Came home, gave them their tea. Bathed them and got them ready for bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Then did they see their parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well they - they didn't always see their father because he wasn't always in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they see their mother regularly at any time during the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, she was always around, you know, somewhere, not far away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have your evening meal when they were in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, afterwards, yes, yes. After they had had theirs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The doctor and his wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - about half past seven I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you see much of the doctor, did you have anything to do with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well he used to come out to feed the dog. I saw him then. Oh he was very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you get to know him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - not too much, he wasn't a man that you could get to know very - very well, but he always treated us very nicely.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said the doctor's wife was only two years older than you, did you get to be friends with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, I was quite friendly with her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did they call you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 By my name. Yes. My own name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was she interested in you, in your personal life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes. She was. Used to talk quite a bit but I always on the points of going and leaving.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well because there was so much to do and as I say she wanted things doing exactly like it had been at the other place where I was and - and there was neither the - the facilities or the - the money I shouldn't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they cook on gas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. They had a range.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Whose job was it to see to that? Was there a bathroom in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Complete with running water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And two - we had two staircases. We always used the back which led up to our bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 At the doctor's house were you allowed to use the bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Oh yes. Just the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How often could you bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - if they were out we used to take a bath then mostly, when the children were in bed and they were out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have any time to yourself during the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, only with the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have holidays to go home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes I believe I did go once. I don't remember going above the once. I think that was the first time I ever went to the seaside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was with her and the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. No, before that. When I went on my own holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And would those holidays be paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't think so. Not there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about uniform there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well - they weren't really as particular as they were at her cousin's house. Just wore a - an apron of course.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Your own clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No we had a - a black dress - the afternoons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember if you had to provide them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I think so. Well I had them you see, from being at the other place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You were there three years but on the point of leaving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I stayed there 'til I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Is that why you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. I left from there to be }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did you get on with the cooks that came and went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Oh - not very well, they weren't very intelligent, any of them. I don't know, she never seemed to come across anyone that was - really very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have any friends then, did you know anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No, except my sister you see, she was at Sands then and - I mustn't say Sands - and another girl had come in my place that came from the same village that we did so - we did used to meet occasionally, three of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you belong to any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. There was very little life in this place as all - no picture house or anything. There was no - nothing to go out for you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you sing in the choir at church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Not there, I did when - I was at home but not - not there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How old were you when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Twenty-four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How long had you known your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - about three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did you meet him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I think really we met - we both went to the same church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was in the village where you were working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you save up money before getting }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, just a little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your parents help you in setting up a home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. But I had a little money of my own, which helped.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How long were you engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I should - about a year I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me about the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had the wedding at home, at my parent's home. At the farm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
 in the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In a church yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who gave you away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 My father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were there many guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, quite a few. Just the family. Just sister and brother and - and my - few of my relations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about wedding presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't think I had very many. I don't remember having much at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. My father made us a lovely meal. He boiled a ham and a lump of beef and made us quite a good send off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That was at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have a honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. But - at that time my husband was having his holiday and we took our honeymoon in days going about the countryside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where were you living at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In the place where I'd been in service, because he lived - he came from that part of the country.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have your own house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we rented it, yes, very nice little house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Just two bedrooms and sitting room and a living kitchen. No bathroom of course. But it was very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you furnish it yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of things did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had a sideboard and - three piece suite and four chairs. Had a nice carpet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did you get those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we paid for them when we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587  so we had a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How many years did you live in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I - three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was it a terraced house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, it was in a row.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was it near the centre of the village?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. It was quite out. It was a walk out of the village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you live after you moved from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well in the same district but we moved into another house. Where we had a small garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How long did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I lived there - I lived there -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was it the same kind of house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Very similar, yes, but it was pleasanter - a nicer outlook.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How long did you live in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I lived there, my husband went to the war from there and came back there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How old was your husband when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Twenty-three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What was his job at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He worked in a dyehouse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that the first job he did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. That was the job that he'd done as far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about afterwards - did he change his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well after he came from the war he wasn't able to go back there and he trained for a shoe repairer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did he do in they dyehouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Dyed pieces of cloth. You, know, putting them into vats of boiling water dye and dying them. And of course on account of his injury during the war he wasn't able to follow his employment so he went to a - Technical school and learnt to be shoe repairer.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he do any part time jobs outside the shoe repairing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that his own business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. He rented a small shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he have anybody work for him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, he just carried on on his own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How do you think he felt about his work, do you think he was sorry to give up the dyeing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, I don't think so, I think he enjoyed this - job altogether. Well that was after - after he'd had his service you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 But on the whole he really liked it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What do you think he liked about it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I think he liked working for himself and it was - quite a new sort of work you see, he was interested in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have any children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How many?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I had - three children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could you tell me the date of birth of those born before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Only one. A boy was born in 1914.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was he born at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you know what to expect in childbirth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not at all. Nothing. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did you get on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have anybody to help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not particularly. I didn't have a trained nurse, she was what we called a midwife at that - you know, in that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was there a doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, yes. Yes, I had a doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was he the doctor you'd worked for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, it was his brother - oh yes, yes. It was. The first one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me a bit about when he was born, do you know how soon you got up after the birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I was in bed about a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did any of your relatives come over and help? Did your step-mother help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - no, she lived too far away. My husband's sister lived next door and she used to come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about neighbours - did you have good neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, very good. Yes
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they actually help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well they'd run errands and things like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you feed this boy yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember about how long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Fourteen months. And he never had anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He went then from breast milk to what?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Food. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you enjoy feeding him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You didn't have any trouble?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you get any advice on what to eat or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, nothing. Except from the midwife.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When he was sleeping would you wake him to feed him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 If he cried did you pick him up and feed him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I'm afraid I did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 If he didn't seem hungry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I'm afraid he always was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember when you took him off milk was it suddenly or bit by bit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
No we - no, he used to start and have vegetables and gravy because you see, just - or a - and a rusk, crust of bread or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 That's how he started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 At that time did you think it was wrong or not to let the baby cry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well, we were always told we shouldn't let a baby boy cry. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 There was no reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about punishment when he was naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think I - I don't remember punishing him much. He was a very good child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 If he was punished what would it be for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't know - I don't remember punishing him at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How much did your husband have to do with this boy when he was under a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh, he played with him a lot. He was very fond of him. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The baby was born before your husband went into the army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. In 1914.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When did your husband go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He went in about 1916.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would he do things for the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Change him and all that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well he'd bath him. And play with him, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 At this time before 1919 did you know what your husband earned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How much of that would he give you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He used to give it me all - gave - give me the wage packet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he have any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, if he wanted anything he - take some. But he always handed - his wage packet over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you discuss with him how you should spend the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, we usually went shopping together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 For big things like furniture, who would buy that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we'd already got that that we wanted, we didn't need anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you ever have anybody living in with you at that time, lodgers or relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember about the clothes and the washing, did you do all the washing at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Always. My own washing, own baking and everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about shoes - were they bought new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Yes. They were bought new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where would you go for that - to the bigger towns?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. About seven miles away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about your husbands help in the house with washing up, cooking and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't think he did. It really wasn't necessary, it was only a small house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 But he did play with the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Yes. You see, he - he was quite late getting home from work you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How far away did he work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh he worked three miles away and he walked. Night and morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So he didn't come home for his dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no, he always had to have it packed up. And sometimes he worked in the night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What did he do about food and things then, did you have a hot tea for him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh when he came home I always cooked him a hot meal at - teatime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about when he was working at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well he'd have a good breakfast and go to bed. Ready for the next - round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember what time the little boy went to bed and where did he sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He had a little room, his room. I'm afraid he didn't go to bed very early, didn't like - anyhow he was very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So he stopped up a bit did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about bathing, you said there was no indoor bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, we used to bath in front of the fire. In a big - a big bath, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you eat your meals in this house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In the living room. Sometimes in the kitchen. In the summer we always ate in the kitchen because it was cooler.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You cooked in this kitchen on what kind of equipment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh we cooked in the living place, on the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 An open fire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. With an oven. Side oven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How would you boil water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 We had a boiler at one side and an oven at the other and it - the fire heated both the oven and the boiler you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was this coal or wood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Coal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 All your meals had to be cooked on that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And all the lighting was paraffin. Paraffin oil.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What kind of lamps were those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had one that stood on the table and we had a hanging lamp. But when we'd been there a few years we put gas in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did that cut the work down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. Hadn't the lamps to clean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said you baked your own bread - what about bottling and jam making?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't think I did a lot of bottling then. Not when I was first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you grow any vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. The garden wasn't big enough. Just a flower garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You didn't keep any hens or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember how many times a week you ate meat?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Ate meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would it be every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I think we had meat or fish every day of some kind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What was breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Bacon or eggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 His packed up lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Then I had to pack him sandwiches to take to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you ever get extra meat from hunting or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was there any tinned food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Tinned? Oh yes. We used to have tinned fruit and salmon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did everybody get equal shares do you think - you were never short?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was he ever out of work - was he ever laid off from the dyeworks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He was before we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587  but not afterwards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he ever work short time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No, he wasn't on short time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did the boy eat with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Could he eat whatever he wanted or did he have to eat up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I'm afraid we weren't very strict with him being the first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was he allowed to have seconds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, if he was - if he wanted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about table manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we always taught them to have manners. Say please and thank you. How to hold their knife and fork.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he sit in a high chair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Beginning, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember if you and your husband agreed on how he was bought up, did one of you spoil him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think so. I'm afraid we both spoiled him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 If you were worried about him who could you talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No one, only the neighbours - a neighbour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about your husband's sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well she wasn't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
 so she didn't know much about babies.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember any special neighbours, was there one person that you could turn to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well it was the woman that I had when - when he was born, she was very good. She lived about two doors away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The midwife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you ever see your step-mother after this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you talk to her about bringing him up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well - there again she'd never had any children. You could talk to her but she didn't know much about children at all. She often used to come over for the day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about other children - did he have other children to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were there any children around that you didn't like him to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about Sundays in your own home, were they different from other days, what did you do on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Used go for a walk I should think, we didn't do much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, on Sunday nights as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you take him with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have special meals on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Well we always had a roast, bigger roast. 'Course the meat was cheap in those days, we could get a good roast for two and sixpence. Of course the wages weren't as big. But - we never seemed short.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about on special occasions like his birthday and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't think we made much difference really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we had the usual decorations you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You didn't go home for Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I think we did once but only once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You'd have special meals and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. See, my husband went away soon afterwards so - I had to look after myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When your husband was still home, what about people coming in - musical evenings and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, at that time no, we didn't.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You didn't have many friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not - no, not where we lived, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he have any family living near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, his sister and - four brothers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you see much of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, they were all very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of things would you do when you got together, would you go to their house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well they'd come in and we'd go there you know. Play games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well, dominoes or ludo or anything like that for the child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did they play musical instruments or dance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. They didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you play games with the boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. I had to do. And take him out of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about your own leisure - did you do a lot of reading or what - sewing, you wouldn't have much leisure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, no, there wasn't muc
h time 'cos when he came home from work he was six o'clock, it was time to get the boy ready for bed and he - get his meal over and I'm afraid we went to bed early those days. Nine o'clock, because he had to be up early.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you get any newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 We had the local paper. Not much else, don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about magazines or books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was he interested in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No, I don't think he was very much. He were more interested in football. In fact, he was a footballer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he continue to play after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 On Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did he play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh a long way off sometimes. I'm afraid I didn't like it. 'Cos all his time was spent away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you ever go to watch him play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember going away on holiday before the war at all after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 ?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think we ever went for a holiday, not to go away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did he get holidays from work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, he had a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What would you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we should go for walks I suppose, and go to the town if there was a - a fair there we should go to the fair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me about these fairs, can you remember what you did, stayed there all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no. No, 
we should just go for the afternoon. I don't think the money ran to, you know, having holidays you know. Not much a week he had - didn't ask how much the wage was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Twenty-seven shillings. When we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 It would be just that 'til he went to the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Didn't change?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And you'd to manage on that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember how much your rent was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Two and six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would there be any other regular charges like rates or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes, there was rates on top of that. And when he went into the army they gave me seventeen and six a week to keep myself and the boy.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did your husband go to clubs at the church and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well he did go to a club - yes. But not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What club would that be - would that be connected with the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, it was a working mans club. But he always - used to be very happy to stay at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about savings clubs and insurance or clothing clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No clothing clubs. But I believe we did have a - an insurance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about a burial club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Were there any concerts or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well just at the church. Used to be a concert - now and gain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When you went out or your relatives called in what would you have to eat and drink - what would you serve them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Just the same that we always had. Might open - extra fruit or something like that. Get a bit of boiled ham or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They'd come in for tea would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would you ask them or would they just drop in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh, we asked them mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You say you rented your home, can you remember who your landlord was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. He was - a man come our house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How did you get on with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 All right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He treated you fairly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. As long as we paid the rent of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The place where you lived after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 , would you say it was a suburb of the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well it was what's called an urban district - urban district. Larger than where I lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 How far was it from the centre of the town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where I lived? Oh only about five minutes walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who would you say were the most important people living there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well the manufacturers, was quite a lot of large mills.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have anything to do with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh I knew them, yes, with going shopping. They were all very nice people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about others like the vicar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. I knew the vicar very well. Very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Which church would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Not the parish - called St Johns. A little church out of the village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You didn't go to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, not then. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of people would you say went to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well all kinds. All kinds of people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would they be the same as those that went to the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, mostly the - I should say the doctors and people like that went to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about chapel?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well there were both sorts as I say, there - there were quite a lot of mills in the place and - some went to one place and some the other.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 The people in the working class where you lived after you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 , were they all the same in their living like they were in the place where you were born or was there a difference in their standard of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, I don't think there was much difference at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would you say there were some very poor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well there'd be one or two families - I daresay. But I - we always used to think that they were people who wouldn't
 help themselves, you know, wouldn't work. There wasn't a lot of poverty because there was such a lot of work. Never shortage of work in that place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would those people be thought of as rough and the others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, I should say so. Just one or two odd families.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of work would they do when they did work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Perhaps - sweeping the roads or - you know, working for the council perhaps, something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well everyone worked in the mills. All the girls as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What sort of jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Some were - weavers and some were menders, which was very clean work and very well paid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What about the men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 They were the same. They were weavers and - of course they had different jo
bs, I don't know really what they did. 'Cos I never went into a mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you think one group of the working people felt superior to the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, only that they thought maids were not as good as they were of course. The mill girls always thou
ght that maids weren't as good as them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I don't know at all. No idea. But they did. I suppose they could earn more money for one thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you think where you got that feeling, did you ever meet mill girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well only when we went out, but they never speak to you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 After you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
 did you ever feel it was a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, as far as I can recollect we always seemed to be - fairly comfortable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Supposing your husband was il
l or out of work - it was only about two years after the baby wars born, can you remember what happened then, did he get paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh no. No, there was no money, if they were out of work they were out of work. There was no dole or anything of that kind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well we just had to spend what we had. We'd saved anything.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember if you did manage to save anything at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, we did manage to save a bit because - after a few years we - put money down to buy a house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 After the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. He didn't smoke and he didn't drink. Very - careful living man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 And that's how you managed to save?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Where did you save - in the Post Office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, the Building Society.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you remember if you started that just after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 When did you start?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 I should say after the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Before that you just saved from week to week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, if I'd anything to save. 'Course I hadn't much while he was in 
the army you see. And then he came home and he was - discharged. And - they gave him so much a week 'til he found something to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 After the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. And of course he'd only been home about - six months when - the boy died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me a little bit about that, what year would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Wait a bit - I should think it was getting on towards the end of the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 1919 wasn't it, he was five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Can you tell me a little bit about his illness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well he never did have an illness 'til he had this last illness and it was - during that 'flu epidemic was going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you have help from your neighbours then or your step-mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh, no - my step-mother, they were too far away, it was just the neighbours that helped.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who came to the funeral then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well my family came. My sister and brother and father and step-mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you wear mourning clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, of course it was the thing to do then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Besides wearing mourning clothes what did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No, only just wearing black.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 For how long?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I think after we'd got them we had to wear them 'til they were done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Before your husband went to the war you used to walk a lot, where did you go, what kind of countryside was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh well, it's very nice, very pretty countryside all around, very hilly. And - we used to take long walks. Especially on Sunday evenings.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you ever make for anywhere like a pub or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 No. No. No, I never remember my husband going to a public house. At all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that because he believed in teetotal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I suppose he must have been made that way, I don't know. He didn't anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you see much of his family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. In fact, they lived next door. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you see much of his brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, he had four brothers. None of them were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 . Not the sister. Oh we saw quite a lot of them. And they all - they all went to the war, the boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What happened to the sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh she stayed at home. She went working in a shop. While - when they were away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What was his father, where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He came from - from the same place and he was a tailor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 In a big way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, quite a big firm. He was a very good tailor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 But he worked for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, he worked for a firm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did any of his boys train to a trade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
Yes, the eldest was a tailor. And - then the next two were - both in shops. The youngest was a butcher. I think my husband was the only one that hadn't a trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 You said he was a dyer - was that something he had to learn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well I suppose yes he - he'd go straight from school there. Dyeing the pieces of cloth. Different shades I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He had to give it up because of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well you see it wa
s working amongst a lot of wet and water all the time and - and of course it was his feet that were badly injured, he had trench feet so that he couldn't - stand about amongst the wet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Do you think he liked his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes, I think he was happy enough there. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What would you say his main interest was, his work or his football or his family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well he was very interested in football, he played for one of the big towns at one time. But - he gave up going a lot after we were }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587  because - I'm afraid I used to complain that he was always off on Saturdays.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 He came from quite a small country district, can you remember what you thought of the town at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well it wasn't a town really, the nearest town from where I lived wa
s seven miles. So we were quite a way off. And at that time there were no buses. Could only go by train and - weren't a lot of trains either.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 So how often would you go to the big town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh - I don't remember going at all much. Except, if she - if the mistress sent me on an errand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Would she send you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Sometimes if she wanted a - anything exchanging.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 What would you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Take it back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 To a big shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Which I didn't like because I was lost in the place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that regularly done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Well not - not often, she used to go herself, quite a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 She must have trusted you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh yes. We had to find our way about you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Was that the farthest you'd ever been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Yes. Yes, I never went further than that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Did you ever go to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Never. First time I went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 was after I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6317369 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 . She used to go a lot - to London.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11671465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Who would be in charge when she went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9778766 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 Oh, just left us, the maids in charge, that's all.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-461\li461\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid11671465 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5112741\charrsid16649587 
\par }}